Products.Name: Apple Air Pods Max | Color Pink

Properties.Name: LongDescription
Properties.Value: A radically original composition. The over-ear headphone has been completely reimagined. From cushion to canopy, AirPods Max are designed for an uncompromising fit that creates the optimal acoustic seal for many different head shapes fully immersing you in every sound. Audio quality Sounds like an epiphany. AirPods Max combine high-fidelity audio with industry-leading Active Noise Cancellation to deliver an unparalleled listening experience. Each part of their custom-built driver works to produce sound with ultra-low distortion across the audible range. From deep, rich bass to accurate mids and crisp, clean highs, you’ll hear every note with a new sense of clarity. Magical experience Elaborately simple. AirPods Max inherit all of the wireless, effortless magic of the AirPods family. With even more tricks in the mix, they make the listening experience completely seamless, so you can find and stay in your groove, day to night.
